# Don't forget to render the markdown as HTML. Some people will download the ZIP, and not be able to render the markdown.
pandoc -s --from gfm README.md -o README.html -V header-includes="<style>body { max-width: none; }</style>"

# To upload to Moodle...
- Download zip from GitLab
- Extract
- Remove sources directory `rm -rf materials-src`, to get around the 200MB Moodle limit
- Compress `zip -r digital-systems.zip digital-systems-main`
- Upload
